  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large clay pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the garlic and saut\u000220 until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, paprika, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper and stir for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cherry tomatoes and stir to coat with the spice mixture.",
    "Add the harissa and stir for 1 minute.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 15 minutes.",
    "Stir in the parsley and lemon juice and serve hot.",
    "Serve the tagine over couscous or with crusty bread.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!",
    "This dish can be made ahead and refrigerated for up to 2 days.",
    "Reheat the tagine over low heat before serving.",
